metadata.author: Yoto
metadata.description: Lyrics can be over-stimulating at night for young listeners, so these instrumental lullabies are a perfect way to bring familiar tunes and relaxing melodies into the bedtime routine. Including classic rhymes beloved by the whole family, everyone will be able to settle down to sleep with this collection of musical lullabies.
